description: You asked for big burly guys. You got it. Tyler Saint is a powerhouse but for some reason or another he doesn't have much luck here on NK. He got injured in his last Live Audience match with Patrick Rouge. Let's see if he learns anything from his previous matches. Mustang exclusive Samuel Colt is back for another match. He overpowered Luke Riley in his last match but does he have what it takes to overcome Tyler Saint?
title: Tyler Saint vs Samuel Colt
